<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 - Página não encontrada | LinkUp</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      background: #121212;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .container { max-width: 520px; }
    .code {
      font-size: 8rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f03e3e, #ff6b6b);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 16px 0 10px; }
    p { color: #888; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-primary {
      background: #f03e3e;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.85; color: white; }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: #aaa;
      border: 1px solid #3a3a3a;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: #f03e3e; color: #f03e3e; }
    .icon { font-size: 3rem; color: #f03e3e; margin-bottom: 8px; display: block; }
    .logo { 
      font-size: 1.2rem; 
      font-weight: 800; 
      color: #f03e3e; 
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <a href="/" class="logo">LinkUp</a>
    <div class="code">404</div>
    <i class="bi bi-search icon"></i>
    <h1>Página não encontrada</h1>
    <p>A página que você está tentando acessar não existe ou foi removida. Verifique o endereço ou volte para a página inicial.</p>
    <div class="actions">
      <a href="/" class="btn-primary"><i class="bi bi-house me-2"></i>Voltar ao início</a>
      <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn-secondary"><i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-2"></i>Voltar</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
